author: artem-mazanov
name: test_4
query:
$QuadkeyPyLib = @@_LIB_quadkey_@@;
$qk = Python::latlon2quadkey("(Double?, Double?, Int32?) -> String?", $QuadkeyPyLib);

$from = '2018-10-01';
$to = '2018-11-30';

INSERT INTO `_OUTPUT_PATH_`
SELECT      day
            , hour
            , qk_from
            , qk_to
            , AVG(driving_distance_m) as avg_dist
            , AVG(driving_duration_sec) as avg_time
            , COUNT(*) as cnt

            , "" as city
            , "2018-01-01" as dt
            , "2018-01-01 00:00:00" as dttm_utc_1_min
            , 0 as ts_1_min

FROM        RANGE([home/taxi-dwh/ods/tracker/candidates], $from, $to)
WHERE       TRUE
AND         driving_distance_m IS NOT NULL
AND         driving_duration_sec IS NOT NULL

AND         lat_from IS NOT NULL
AND         lon_from IS NOT NULL
AND         lat_to IS NOT NULL
AND         lon_to IS NOT NULL

AND         lat_middle IS NULL
AND         lon_middle IS NULL
GROUP BY    $qk(lat_from, lon_from, 16) as qk_from
            , $qk(lat_to, lon_to, 16) as qk_to
            , DateTime::GetDayOfWeek(DateTime::TimestampFromStringFormat(utc_start_dttm, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')) as day
            , DateTime::GetHour(DateTime::TimestampFromStringFormat(utc_start_dttm, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')) as hour

_LIMIT_
